div.div:
feat(upload): enhance upload service with dependency injection for storage providers
- Refactored NewUploadService to accept storage providers as a parameter. - Implemented cleanup logic for abandoned uploads with improved logging. - Updated CreateUploadSession to ensure atomic operations and handle session IDs more effectively. - Improved findOrCreatePath function for better path management and error handling. - Added zombie entity detection in CreateOrUpdate method of file repository. - Enhanced error handling and logging throughout the upload process. - Updated main.go to initialize storage providers based on settings.

feat: Enhance repository interfaces and implement orphaned entity cleanup
- Added `FindOrphaned` and `HardDelete` methods to `EntityRepository` for managing orphaned entities. - Introduced `SyncItem` struct in `FileRepository` to handle file state during listing. - Implemented `HardDelete` and `CreateOrUpdate` methods in `fileRepository` for better file management. - Updated `mysql.go` to change log level to Info for better visibility. - Refactored `albumRepository` to remove unnecessary dependencies and streamline album handling. - Added new task scheduling functionality for cleaning up abandoned uploads. - Implemented logging and panic recovery wrappers for scheduled tasks. - Created a new `IsExist` method in `LocalProvider` to check file existence. - Removed unused image file from storage.

feat: Implement file operations service with copy, move, delete, rename, and create functionalities
- Added `file_op_service.go` to handle file operations including CopyItems, MoveItems, DeleteItems, RenameItem, and CreateEmptyFile. - Implemented recursive copying of files and folders with conflict checks. - Added functionality to move files and folders with permission and conflict checks. - Implemented deletion of files and folders recursively, including handling of entity reference counts. - Added renaming functionality with checks for existing names and physical renaming in storage. - Created `file_query_service.go` for querying files by URI and retrieving file information. - Implemented folder size calculation and view configuration updates in `file_query_service.go`. - Added utility functions in `file_util_service.go` for handling file operations, including download URL generation and entity reference management.
feat: 重构上传逻辑，优化文件上传流程，添加路径创建锁以解决后端死锁问题，支持系统文件过滤

feat: Implement chunked file upload with session management
- Added BaseUploader abstract class to define common interface for upload tasks. - Created ChunkUploader class to handle individual file chunk uploads. - Implemented SessionUploader class for creating upload sessions and managing chunk sizes. - Introduced a Pool class to manage concurrent upload tasks and prevent duplicate processing. - Enhanced file management hooks to support resumable uploads and error handling. - Updated UploadItem interface to include chunkSize for precise progress tracking. - Improved user interface for file uploads, including error messages and status displays. - Refactored existing upload logic to integrate new uploader classes and maintain clean code structure.
